Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Good afternoon! This is Alex from TerraVista Properties. How may I assist you today?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Hi Alex, I'm looking to buy a house, but I'm a bit overwhelmed with the options out there.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I understand! It can be daunting. What are some of your key requirements and preferences for a new home?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Well, we're a family of four, so we need at least three bedrooms, and it would be great to have a backyard for the kids. We also prefer a quiet neighborhood with good schools.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That makes sense. Do you have a specific budget in mind?

Speaker: Customer
Text: We're looking to stay within the $400,000 to $450,000 range.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Perfect, we have several properties that might match your criteria. Have you had a chance to go through our listings online?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, but I'm not seeing anything that really fits what we're looking for. Most of the homes in our budget are either too small or not in the right areas.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I hear you. Sometimes the online listings don't capture everything. Have you considered slightly expanding your search radius or looking at homes that might need a little cosmetic work?

Speaker: Customer
Text: We're open to it, but we really don't want a fixer-upper since we don't have the time or expertise for any major renovations.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Understandable. How about newly constructed homes? They often come at a premium, but there might be some room to negotiate, especially in the current market.

Speaker: Customer
Text: We did think about new constructions, but they're usually more expensive and the wait times can be long. We need to move in within the next three months.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Got it. Let me make a few notes here. I believe I have a couple of properties in our inventory that could be a good match. How about we schedule a tour for this weekend?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Sure, that sounds good. Do you have anything available in the Maplewood area?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Yes, we have a few listings in Maplewood that fit your criteria. I can arrange for us to visit those first. Would Saturday at 10 AM work for you?

Speaker: Customer
Text: That works for us.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great! I'll set it up and send you a confirmation email with all the details. Is there anything else you'd like to discuss before our meeting?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Not at the moment. I appreciate your help, Alex.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: My pleasure! Looking forward to meeting you on Saturday. Have a great day!

Speaker: Customer
Text: You too. Thanks!
